A collection of reference questions pulled from the proposed EU Digital Legal Personality Registration
(completion percentage: 10%)

Section 1 - White Paper Compliance 

 Definition and Basic Exemption
  The legislation states  state “ a document in such form and containing such information as specified in article 4  and First Schedule"
  Certain information specified in this Schedule may be omitted from the whitepaper if: 
  (a) disclosure of such information would be contrary to the public interest;
  (b) disclosure of such information would be seriously detrimental to the issuer, provided that the omission would not be likely 
  to mislead the public with regard to facts and circumstances essential for an informed assessment of the prospects of the
  issuer, the proposed project and of the features of the virtual financial assets to which the whitepaper relates;
  (c) such information is of minor importance only for a specific offer and is not information that will influence an informed 
  assessment of the prospects of the issuer, the proposed project and of the features of the virtual financial
  assets to which the whitepaper relates; or
  (d) disclosure of such information is found to be inappropriate to the issuer’s sphere
  of activity or proposed activity, as the case may be, or its legal form or to
  the virtual financial assets being offered, in which case the
  Whitepaper shall contain equivalent information
  when available.notices or terms not stated in White Paper or a properly published Addendum Shall be void
  
  Questions:
  Is the whitepaper dated?
  y or n 
  If not date whitepaper and proceed
 
  Does the whitepaper contain a non-technical introductory summary?
  y or n 
  If not provide summary and proceed.
  *Note* for the purposes of this summary "key information" means essential and appropriately structured information
  which is to be
  provided to investors with a view to enabling them to understand the nature and
  the risks of the proposed project, the issuer and the virtual financial assets
  that are being offered to them.
  
  Does the white paper include the names and roles of the persons who wrote or contribute to the white paper?
  y or n
  If not includes names and roles of drafters of white paper and proceed.
  
  Is the purpose of the arrangement clearly explained?
  y or n
  If not include purpose in white paper and proceed.
  
  Are there any activities or actions taken by the prospective ITA that take place off the blockchain listed in the white paper?  
  y or n  
  If no follow up question  
  Do any activities take place off ot the blockchain?  
  y or n
  if yes explain procedure and persons or organizations responsible for procedures which occur off of the blockchain.

  Is there technical a description of the protocol, platform and/or functionality of the virtual token or virtual financial asset.
  y or n
  If not include technical description and proceed.
  
  Is there a detailed description of the sustainability and scalability of the proposed project included in the white paper?
  y or n
  If not include forward looking plan and proceed.
  *Note* registering a technical arrangment implies to the authority an intent to exist into the future for some time unless a completion
  or finalization date is included.  The authority assumes a competent strucure so that complaince can be maintained during growth 
  or transfers or administrative responsibility as well as being interested in seeing the sustainability of the concept from a general 
  perspective.
  
  Is there a clear and well thought out analysis of challenges and risks for achieving tghe stated purpose of the organization?
  y or n
  If not include the technology specific disclaimer of challenges and risks.
  
  Is there a detailed description of the charecteristics and the functionality being offered.
  y or n
  If not include charecteristics and functionality of any tokens of virtual financial assets owned or controlled by 
  the technology arrangement.
  
  Does the white paper list who issues the token or virtual financial assets?
  y or n
  If not list issuer(s)
  
  Does the white paper include names of the development team?
  y or n
  If not list development team members.
  
  Does the white paper list any formal advisors?
  y or n
  If n follow up question
   Does the the applicant have any formal adivsors?
   y or n
   If yes then include formal advisors in the white paper
   
  Does the white paper list any service providers whom it depend on to perform tasks for applicant?
  y or n
  If no include names of any and all service providers
  *Note* in all situations there should be at least one an independent systems auditor, typically there will be more than one.
  
  Is there a detailed description of the type and of wallet(s) used by any issuers? (only if yes to issuers)
  y or n
  if n provide detailed description of issuers wallet type.
  
  Is there a detailed description of the security methods in place to protect issuers wallet(s)
  y or n
  If no provide description of security measures taken to protect issuers wallet(s)
  
  Are there security measure listed in the white paper which are taken to protect the integrity of the protocol against 
  cyber attacks or hacks which is consistant with industry best practices?
  y or n
  If no include description of protocol security measure and methods for protecting integrity of the protocol.
  
  Does the white paper include a detailed description of the life cycle of the initial virtual financial asset offering and
  the proposed project?
  y or n
  If n include anticipated project length, maturity length, and any other timelines as is relevant with regard to the offering
  
  Is there a detailed description of future milestones?
  y or n
  If no include list of future milestones
  
  Is there a detailed description stating how the project has been and will continue to be financed
  y or n
  If no include description of sources of financing and funding method for continued opporations for the duration of the 
  life cycle of the product or offering
  
  Are there details regarding targeted purchasers, acquirers, holders, or investors in the platform and its token?
  y or n
  If not include targeted audience, consumer, investor, etc.
  
  Is there a description of the manner funds raised through the initial virtual financial asset offering
  will be allocated?
  y or n
  If n include such description fo how any funds raised will be allocated
  
  Is there a the detailed description of total number of virtual financial assets to be issued (hard cap/soft cap) if applicable?
  y or n
  If not include min/max supply information
  
  Is there a detailed description of how and when any tokens or virtual financial assets will be distributed?
  y or n
  if n then include distribution information
  
  Is there a description of the concensus algorithem used by the protocol (if applicable)
  y or n
  if no include cryptographic hash concensus algorithem type
  
 Is there a detailed description of any incentive mechanisms used to secure any transactions(mining), transaction and/ or any other applicable
 fees; as well as a best estimated of the speed of transactions?
 y or n
 If no include information about transaction processing, mining, and transaction/network speeds.
 
 Is tax information clearly laid out?
 *Note* Organization and persons which earn money, assets or value in any jurisdiction pay taxes.  
  y or n
  If no include tax structure for the organiztion.
    
  Does the whitepaper list the known or anticipated Euro exchange rate to the token or virtual financial asset?
  y or n
  If no include information on valuation in Euros.
  
  Is there a detailed description of the smart contract?
  y or n
  if no include detailed description of the smart contract.
  
  Is there a detailed description of the the adopted standards, as well as that of any underlying
  protocol/s,functionality/-ies and associated operational costs or gas fees?
  y or n
  If no include detailed description of standards and protocols and their costs or gas fees.
 
   Is there a detailed description of the underlying protocol’s interoperability with other protocols?
  y or n
  If not include base protocol and associate protocol information.
  
  Is the name of the Registered System's Auditor, and link to the information provided by the Registered System's Auditor 
  included in the whitepaper?
  y or n
  If not include link to audit documentation as provided by a registered systems auditor.
  
  Does the whitepaper include a list of any applicable restrictions either by declaration or embedded in the smart contract/s 
  deployed, if any, including any investment and/or geographical restrictions?
  y or n
  If no include list of applicable restriction to the any offerings.
  
  Does the whitepaper describe any methods or program administrators, agents, or others use to obtain data and verify occurrences
  from smart contracts (also known as ‘oracles’) used and detailed description of their characteristics and functionality thereof?
  y or no
 
  Is there any restrictions on the free transferability of the virtual financial assets being offered and the DLT exchange/s on which they
  may be traded, to the extent known by the issuer?
  y or n
  If yes explain any restrictions.
 
 Is there a detailed description of the methods of payment; the participants of any potnetial financial asset offering will be able to get their contribution
 back if the soft cap is not reached at the end of the offering and detailed description of the refund mechanism, including the expected time-line of when
 such refund will be completed?
 y or n
 If no explain investor return procedures for projects wghich do not reach their soft cap.
 
 Is there a detailed description of the risks associated with the virtual financial assets and the investment therein?
 y or n
 If no include detailed description of risks associated with the potential investment or virtual financial asset.
 
 Are there any right of pre-emption associated with the offering or any other offer of first rights to paerticipate in or acquire something?
 y or n
 If yes follow up question
 Is the procedure clearly laid out for the right of pre-emption offered?
 y or n
 If no include procedure associated with special rights to participate or acquire first offered in the whtiepaper.
 
 Is there a description and clear terms of any bonuses or discounts being offered?
 y or n
 If no include description of any bonuses or discounts being offered and the terms.
 
 









  
  
  



  
  




  
  
  
  
  
  


  
 



